      "description": "Offered is a superlative example of the E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS. This vehicle is mechanically pristine; the critical rod bearing service and rear subframe reinforcement have been completed to ensure peak structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile, short-throw engagement, directing power through a variable M-differential lock. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping characteristics with zero bushing deflection, preserving the chassis's renowned neutral handling balance. The exterior finish is concours-quality, showing no signs of oxidation or paint correction needs. A turn-key acquisition for the purist seeking an uncompromised driving experience.",
